\section{Analysis}
This section will analyse the potential for biometric measurements on the
\textit{Apple Watch}. The analysis will cover both the hardware itself and how
it is utilized by the software.

\subsection{Hardware}
The \textit{Apple Watch} includes a multitude of sensors \cite{watchspecs}, which is used for
different purposes. The sensors are mostly used for activity and fitness 
tracking, but they are also used for some security functionalities.




